  <metadata>
    <name>Tour 13: Kinzigtal &amp; Gutachtal</name>
    <desc>Explore the central Black Forest’s most scenic valleys—the Kinzigtal and Gutachtal—with their traditional farmhouses, half-timbered towns, and the famous Vogtsbauernhof open-air museum.</desc>
    <author>
      <name>Hockenheim Motorcycle Tours</name>
    </author>
  </metadata>
